pageTitle: Cornerstone University Athletics - 2010 Women's Soccer Roster
textBeforeTable: Women's Soccer Roster   Personal - Melissa is the daughter of Dan & Kathi McIntire of Papua, New Guinea. High School - Melissa played soccer for 4 years at Numonohi Christian Academy in Papua, New Guinea. She was voted team MVP in both her junior and senior seasons.
